implementation_notes:
Running totals and period-to-date:
```dax
// Year-to-date
VulnCount YTD = TOTALYTD([VulnCount], 'DateTable'[Date])

// Fiscal YTD (fiscal year ends September 30)
VulnCount FYTD = TOTALYTD([VulnCount], 'DateTable'[Date], "09-30")

// Quarter-to-date
VulnCount QTD = TOTALQTD([VulnCount], 'DateTable'[Date])

// Cumulative running total from first period
VulnCount Running =
    VAR _Key = MAX('DateTable'[MonthSort])
    RETURN CALCULATE([VulnCount], FILTER(ALL('DateTable'), 'DateTable'[MonthSort] <= _Key))
```
